4
00:02:28,160 --> 00:02:28,630
Let's go.

5
00:02:28,630 --> 00:02:30,160
Someone, take him down.

6
00:02:30,160 --> 00:02:31,550
I am Qi Menglin,
the Deputy Commandant of Pingyangwei.

7
00:02:32,190 --> 00:02:33,960
My father is the Governor of Shanxi.

8
00:02:34,390 --> 00:02:35,270
Who dares to touch me?

9
00:02:37,360 --> 00:02:38,190
So what?

10
00:02:38,440 --> 00:02:39,800
This is my lady's gathering.

11
00:02:39,910 --> 00:02:41,000
What right do you have to disturb it?

12
00:02:41,190 --> 00:02:42,750
Your lady hasn't said anything yet.

13
00:02:43,240 --> 00:02:44,630
Who are you to speak?

14
00:02:45,030 --> 00:02:46,160
A barking dog does not bite.

15
00:02:50,750 --> 00:02:51,750
Mr. Qi,

16
00:02:52,080 --> 00:02:53,160
what are you doing?

17
00:02:53,390 --> 00:02:55,360
We're just here for fun.

18
00:02:56,030 --> 00:02:57,190
We asked Jin Nang

19
00:02:57,240 --> 00:02:58,630
to showcase her skills.

20
00:02:58,960 --> 00:03:00,520
Everyone is here to enjoy.

21
00:03:00,800 --> 00:03:03,440
We didn't mean to offend you.

22
00:03:03,750 --> 00:03:04,800
Miss Liu,

23
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:06,550
you truly are a refined lady.

24
00:03:07,270 --> 00:03:08,600
You really have good upbringing.

25
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:10,960
You haven't even married yet,

26
00:03:10,960 --> 00:03:11,880
and you're already in such a hurry,

27
00:03:11,880 --> 00:03:12,830
taking charge

28
00:03:12,830 --> 00:03:13,910
at Magistrate Han's place.

29
00:03:14,270 --> 00:03:15,030
Your father didn't teach you

30
00:03:15,030 --> 00:03:15,800
about propriety and honor?

31
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:17,360
Do you not know
what it means to be educated and polite?

32
00:03:18,110 --> 00:03:19,190
It's okay if you don't understand.

33
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:21,240
Just go home and learn.

34
00:03:23,240 --> 00:03:24,360
You reckless fool.

35
00:03:24,830 --> 00:03:26,030
I'm the fool?

36
00:03:27,080 --> 00:03:28,190
You're a shrew.

37
00:03:31,110 --> 00:03:32,080
Look at all of you.

38
00:03:32,080 --> 00:03:33,390
You flatter the powerful
and kick the downed.

39
00:03:33,390 --> 00:03:34,630
You're all so petty and spiteful.

40
00:03:35,320 --> 00:03:37,030
You think by flattering someone,

41
00:03:37,550 --> 00:03:39,030
you'll rise to greatness?

42
00:03:39,520 --> 00:03:40,750
You think your worth will double?

43
00:03:41,600 --> 00:03:42,960
You're all dressed up,

44
00:03:42,960 --> 00:03:44,190
but have no insight at all.

45
00:03:44,800 --> 00:03:45,800
You actually came to the yamen

46
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:48,630
to listen to a constable play music?

47
00:03:49,080 --> 00:03:49,600
What a joke!

48
00:03:49,600 --> 00:03:50,750
Isn't that laughable?

49
00:03:52,830 --> 00:03:54,910
Those from Mingke House
are nothing but lowly.

50
00:03:55,670 --> 00:03:57,440
All they can do is play music and sing.

51
00:03:57,550 --> 00:03:58,960
They just seduce men.

52
00:03:59,240 --> 00:04:01,240
We're already giving her
too much credit.

53
00:04:02,160 --> 00:04:03,830
The lotus
grows out of the mud unstained.

54
00:04:05,080 --> 00:04:06,720
You're all just vulgar and showy people.

55
00:04:06,960 --> 00:04:08,270
You'd be lucky
to end up in Mingke House.

56
00:04:08,630 --> 00:04:09,720
You wouldn't even get

57
00:04:09,720 --> 00:04:10,440
to play music or sing there.

58
00:04:13,080 --> 00:04:14,110
Wild quails in the ditch

59
00:04:14,110 --> 00:04:15,550
have no right
to laugh at the wild geese above.

60
00:04:20,920 --> 00:04:21,720
If you want to play,

61
00:04:22,230 --> 00:04:22,920
play for me.

62
00:04:23,790 --> 00:04:24,950
No need to waste your talents.

63
00:04:26,160 --> 00:04:26,950
They won't understand.

64
00:04:27,830 --> 00:04:28,390
Let's go.

65
00:04:37,160 --> 00:04:37,760
Aren't you the self-proclaimed

66
00:04:37,760 --> 00:04:39,160
virtuous gentleman?

67
00:04:40,640 --> 00:04:41,550
A virtuous gentleman wouldn't

68
00:04:41,550 --> 00:04:42,550
boast so recklessly.

69
00:04:43,070 --> 00:04:44,600
Don't make promises you can't keep.

70
00:04:45,160 --> 00:04:46,230
Don't mess with those

71
00:04:47,200 --> 00:04:48,200
you can't protect.

72
00:04:59,070 --> 00:05:00,230
You want to be his concubine?

73
00:05:02,270 --> 00:05:03,000
If you're not going to be his concubine,

74
00:05:03,000 --> 00:05:04,200
why did you degrade yourself?

75
00:05:05,720 --> 00:05:06,760
Facing Liu Wan, you swallowed your pride

76
00:05:06,760 --> 00:05:07,920
and did whatever she said.

77
00:05:08,440 --> 00:05:09,440
You were acting like

78
00:05:09,760 --> 00:05:10,350
a lowly concubine

79
00:05:10,350 --> 00:05:11,550
serving the main wife.

80
00:05:11,790 --> 00:05:12,510
The Luo Shu I know

81
00:05:12,510 --> 00:05:13,510
would never act like this.

82
00:05:18,480 --> 00:05:19,270
Am I now

83
00:05:21,510 --> 00:05:23,480
just a big joke?

84
00:05:28,640 --> 00:05:29,830
Han Muzhi is a joke.

85
00:05:31,920 --> 00:05:33,110
He couldn't even speak

86
00:05:33,440 --> 00:05:34,440
in front of Mr. Liu's daughter.

87
00:05:34,790 --> 00:05:36,070
He has no backbone at all.

88
00:05:38,550 --> 00:05:39,390
If you're angry,

89
00:05:39,830 --> 00:05:41,040
I can beat him up for you.

90
00:05:41,790 --> 00:05:42,640
Don't blame him.

91
00:05:44,160 --> 00:05:45,720
It's my own fault
for not seeing clearly.

92
00:05:47,110 --> 00:05:48,760
If I had supported him earlier,

93
00:05:49,950 --> 00:05:50,670
he wouldn't be

94
00:05:50,670 --> 00:05:52,110
so conflicted and pained.

95
00:05:53,920 --> 00:05:55,270
He's blind to what he has.

96
00:05:56,270 --> 00:05:57,390
He doesn't know how to cherish you.

97
00:05:57,390 --> 00:05:58,670
He will regret it for a lifetime.

98
00:06:00,510 --> 00:06:01,670
For two lifetimes, three lifetimes.

99
00:06:02,200 --> 00:06:03,000
In short,

100
00:06:03,200 --> 00:06:04,320
anyone who doesn't cherish you

101
00:06:04,320 --> 00:06:05,480
will always regret it.

102
00:06:19,320 --> 00:06:24,110
Maintain order.

103
00:06:26,790 --> 00:06:27,950
Who are you?

104
00:06:28,230 --> 00:06:29,270
Why did you beat the drum?

105
00:06:29,550 --> 00:06:31,950
Your Honor, my name is Lv Cong.

106
00:06:32,320 --> 00:06:34,110
I am the son
of Lv Wanchang from this county.

107
00:06:34,550 --> 00:06:36,110
My father was imprisoned

108
00:06:36,110 --> 00:06:37,390
due to the case of Ma Tianjin's murder.

109
00:06:37,510 --> 00:06:39,440
I'm here to seek justice for him.

110
00:06:46,760 --> 00:06:48,160
I remember this case.

111
00:06:48,720 --> 00:06:49,480
Ma Tianjin

112
00:06:49,480 --> 00:06:51,270
was killed by a knife at night.

113
00:06:52,070 --> 00:06:53,440
At that time, someone testified

114
00:06:53,670 --> 00:06:55,510
that your father
had a longstanding grudge with him.

115
00:06:55,880 --> 00:06:57,320
Thus, he was accused of murder.

116
00:06:57,670 --> 00:06:58,880
Lv Wanchang

117
00:06:59,480 --> 00:07:00,790
has already confessed.

118
00:07:01,070 --> 00:07:03,440
My father had
deep-seated grievances with Ma Tianjin.

119
00:07:03,510 --> 00:07:04,600
The whole neighborhood knows.

120
00:07:04,600 --> 00:07:06,550
Ma Tianjin died unexpectedly.

121
00:07:06,920 --> 00:07:08,320
Everyone looked at us suspiciously.

122
00:07:08,510 --> 00:07:09,920
My father had no way to defend himself.

123
00:07:10,230 --> 00:07:11,790
To protect his family,

124
00:07:11,790 --> 00:07:12,830
he had no choice but to confess.

125
00:07:13,440 --> 00:07:15,200
Now I have found evidence

126
00:07:15,230 --> 00:07:16,790
that can prove my father's innocence.

127
00:07:17,040 --> 00:07:18,760
If you can't present solid proof,

128
00:07:19,320 --> 00:07:20,920
don't blame me for charging you

129
00:07:21,320 --> 00:07:22,880
with disturbing the court.

130
00:07:23,110 --> 00:07:24,760
I'm here today to reopen the case,

131
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:26,200
and I have undeniable evidence.

132
00:07:29,040 --> 00:07:30,230
Please take a look, Your Honor.

133
00:07:38,040 --> 00:07:39,320
This is a notice

134
00:07:39,350 --> 00:07:41,270
I obtained from my relatives

135
00:07:41,270 --> 00:07:42,440
at Hejin Yamen.

136
00:07:42,720 --> 00:07:44,040
It is copied faithfully.

137
00:07:44,160 --> 00:07:45,110
If there are any fabrications,

138
00:07:45,480 --> 00:07:47,000
I will accept punishment.

139
00:07:48,200 --> 00:07:49,350
In Hejin County last month,

140
00:07:49,390 --> 00:07:50,720
over ten bandits were captured.

141
00:07:50,880 --> 00:07:52,390
Among them, two confessed

142
00:07:52,640 --> 00:07:54,230
that they had
broken into Ma's place to rob

143
00:07:54,390 --> 00:07:55,760
and killed Ma Tianjin.

144
00:07:56,200 --> 00:07:57,550
My father is innocent.

145
00:07:58,160 --> 00:08:00,110
I ask you, Your Honor, to see the truth.

146
00:08:23,440 --> 00:08:25,040
Miss Luo, are you tired?

147
00:08:25,040 --> 00:08:26,480
Take a break. I'll do it.

148
00:08:26,720 --> 00:08:28,160
No, thanks.

149
00:08:29,200 --> 00:08:29,920
Miss Luo,

150
00:08:29,920 --> 00:08:31,670
this work never ends.

151
00:08:31,670 --> 00:08:33,280
When you're feeling down,

152
00:08:33,280 --> 00:08:34,670
you need to take care of yourself.

153
00:08:35,640 --> 00:08:36,470
I know.

154
00:08:36,910 --> 00:08:38,230
You always know better.

155
00:08:39,350 --> 00:08:41,000
Miss Luo, just hold on a few more days.

156
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:42,350
Once Miss Liu leaves,

157
00:08:42,350 --> 00:08:43,320
things will settle down.

158
00:08:48,960 --> 00:08:49,790
How could

159
00:08:49,790 --> 00:08:50,960
such a thing happen?

160
00:08:51,640 --> 00:08:53,230
And it involves Hejin County.

161
00:08:53,350 --> 00:08:54,640
I'm also baffled.

162
00:08:55,110 --> 00:08:56,200
When the case was tried that day,

163
00:08:56,470 --> 00:08:57,280
the facts were clear.

164
00:08:57,280 --> 00:08:58,520
Lv Wanchang confessed.

165
00:08:59,230 --> 00:09:00,230
I believe

166
00:09:00,350 --> 00:09:01,400
the ruling made that day

167
00:09:01,400 --> 00:09:02,320
was appropriate.

168
00:09:02,440 --> 00:09:03,470
It's best

169
00:09:03,880 --> 00:09:05,670
to resolve this case swiftly.

170
00:09:06,400 --> 00:09:08,080
Don't let it
escalate to the higher office.

171
00:09:08,960 --> 00:09:09,910
Otherwise,

172
00:09:11,520 --> 00:09:12,320
it may affect

173
00:09:12,320 --> 00:09:14,080
your career prospects.

174
00:09:15,790 --> 00:09:16,550
Yes.

175
00:09:18,470 --> 00:09:20,230
Your arrival in Linfen

176
00:09:20,350 --> 00:09:22,550
is just the first step in your career.

177
00:09:22,710 --> 00:09:25,000
It's to build your achievements

178
00:09:25,320 --> 00:09:27,000
to help you rise in the future.

179
00:09:27,840 --> 00:09:31,710
You must distinguish between priorities.

180
00:09:32,150 --> 00:09:33,350
Don't sweat the small stuff.

181
00:09:33,350 --> 00:09:35,080
Those trivial matters

182
00:09:35,080 --> 00:09:36,840
can consume a lot of energy.

183
00:09:37,640 --> 00:09:38,670
If real problems arise,

184
00:09:38,670 --> 00:09:39,840
like this case,

185
00:09:40,910 --> 00:09:42,400
you'll dig yourself a hole.

186
00:09:42,910 --> 00:09:44,080
You'll give others a reason
to take advantage of you.

187
00:09:44,640 --> 00:09:45,550
It's a thankless job.

188
00:09:45,550 --> 00:09:47,470
But matters concerning the people
are important,

189
00:09:47,640 --> 00:09:49,440
and I just want to stand up for them.

190
00:09:51,550 --> 00:09:53,440
This is all just talk for others.

191
00:09:54,550 --> 00:09:56,470
If you even believe it yourself,

192
00:09:57,760 --> 00:09:59,440
that's quite foolish.

193
00:10:01,840 --> 00:10:02,790
You've been in Linfen

194
00:10:02,790 --> 00:10:04,960
for over a year now.

195
00:10:05,840 --> 00:10:07,670
Look at the cases you've handled.

196
00:10:08,670 --> 00:10:10,760
Half of them are related to lust.

197
00:10:11,760 --> 00:10:13,710
Does that sound good to you?

198
00:10:15,520 --> 00:10:16,550
I also heard

199
00:10:17,030 --> 00:10:21,110
that you paid to relocate
the graves of the victims

200
00:10:21,910 --> 00:10:24,000
so the couple could be buried together.

201
00:10:24,350 --> 00:10:25,910
That's because
this person helped the yamen

202
00:10:25,910 --> 00:10:27,200
clear out the mining gang's minions.

203
00:10:27,200 --> 00:10:27,910
He deserved credit.

204
00:10:27,910 --> 00:10:29,200
No matter what the reason,

205
00:10:29,590 --> 00:10:31,230
that's not something a magistrate

206
00:10:31,230 --> 00:10:32,670
should have done.

207
00:10:33,670 --> 00:10:34,710
I heard that yesterday

208
00:10:34,880 --> 00:10:37,000
that reckless Mr. Qi

209
00:10:37,280 --> 00:10:39,080
caused a scene at Wan's gathering

210
00:10:39,400 --> 00:10:41,280
because of a courtesan.

211
00:10:41,520 --> 00:10:42,590
Is this true?

212
00:10:43,150 --> 00:10:44,030
Yes, it is.

213
00:10:47,150 --> 00:10:48,880
As the magistrate of Linfen,

214
00:10:49,470 --> 00:10:51,550
arguing with someone in public

215
00:10:52,110 --> 00:10:53,520
is indeed not advisable.

216
00:10:54,840 --> 00:10:56,640
However, your inaction

217
00:10:57,280 --> 00:10:58,280
has truly

218
00:10:59,150 --> 00:11:01,200
caused Wan some grievances.

219
00:11:02,150 --> 00:11:04,880
You and Wan are not formally married,

220
00:11:05,030 --> 00:11:06,080
but in name,

221
00:11:06,080 --> 00:11:08,280
she is already your wife.

222
00:11:08,880 --> 00:11:12,000
As her father,

223
00:11:13,590 --> 00:11:15,080
I do not wish for my daughter

224
00:11:15,840 --> 00:11:17,840
to suffer any more grievances.

225
00:11:26,470 --> 00:11:28,080
Muzhi,

226
00:11:29,710 --> 00:11:30,790
I have always regarded you

227
00:11:30,790 --> 00:11:32,670
favorably.

228
00:11:34,080 --> 00:11:35,440
I have even considered

229
00:11:35,520 --> 00:11:37,440
betrothing my daughter to you.

230
00:11:41,030 --> 00:11:42,470
Do not let me down.

231
00:11:44,280 --> 00:11:44,880
Yes.

232
00:11:52,790 --> 00:11:53,520
Muzhi.

233
00:11:57,910 --> 00:11:59,790
What did Mr. Liu say?

234
00:12:00,200 --> 00:12:01,550
He said everything.

235
00:12:03,520 --> 00:12:05,110
He pointed out all my actions

236
00:12:05,110 --> 00:12:06,000
and details of the case

237
00:12:06,000 --> 00:12:07,710
in the yamen.

238
00:12:08,520 --> 00:12:10,280
He was thorough.

239
00:12:11,080 --> 00:12:12,350
If it weren't for my men

240
00:12:12,350 --> 00:12:13,320
acting as informants,

241
00:12:13,320 --> 00:12:15,230
how could he know so much?

242
00:12:17,350 --> 00:12:18,440
That's not surprising.

243
00:12:19,150 --> 00:12:20,110
It's always the case

244
00:12:20,400 --> 00:12:22,640
that the magistrates come and go
while the petty officials remain.

245
00:12:23,030 --> 00:12:24,710
A magistrate leaves when his term ends,

246
00:12:24,840 --> 00:12:26,350
but these petty officials in the yamen

247
00:12:26,350 --> 00:12:27,910
have often been there for decades,

248
00:12:27,960 --> 00:12:29,760
even passed down through generations.

249
00:12:29,760 --> 00:12:31,110
Naturally, they form their own factions

250
00:12:31,400 --> 00:12:32,320
and have

251
00:12:32,320 --> 00:12:34,520
their own
considerations and calculations.

252
00:12:35,910 --> 00:12:36,470
I cannot

253
00:12:36,470 --> 00:12:38,280
live under constant surveillance.

254
00:12:40,350 --> 00:12:41,150
Meiqing,

255
00:12:43,030 --> 00:12:44,550
I want to rectify the situation.

256
00:12:45,640 --> 00:12:46,520
No, Muzhi.

257
00:12:48,710 --> 00:12:50,030
Do not act rashly.

258
00:12:50,200 --> 00:12:51,640
Otherwise, if it fails,

259
00:12:51,640 --> 00:12:53,350
you might suffer for it.

260
00:12:58,280 --> 00:12:58,910
Alright.

261
00:13:00,470 --> 00:13:01,520
This matter

262
00:13:01,520 --> 00:13:02,760
can be discussed later.

263
00:13:03,280 --> 00:13:05,320
Right now, the most important thing

264
00:13:05,350 --> 00:13:07,280
is to thoroughly investigate
the murder of Ma Tianjin

265
00:13:07,280 --> 00:13:09,230
and the case
of Lv Wanchang's son seeking justice.

266
00:13:10,230 --> 00:13:10,960
Indeed.

267
00:13:10,960 --> 00:13:12,670
If this case is not resolved,

268
00:13:12,670 --> 00:13:13,670
it will be a stain

269
00:13:13,670 --> 00:13:14,760
on your tenure in Linfen.

270
00:13:17,670 --> 00:13:19,230
The evidence from Lv Cong's recantation

271
00:13:19,230 --> 00:13:20,470
comes from Hejin County.

272
00:13:22,000 --> 00:13:23,350
You must send someone immediately

273
00:13:23,470 --> 00:13:25,030
with my name card and travel permit

274
00:13:25,030 --> 00:13:26,280
to Hejin.

275
00:13:28,110 --> 00:13:28,670
Understood.

276
00:13:30,080 --> 00:13:31,110
Welcome back, Cai.

277
00:13:31,640 --> 00:13:32,320
Baozi!

278
00:13:32,550 --> 00:13:34,230
Make some pancakes
for me this afternoon.

279
00:13:34,320 --> 00:13:35,030
Tomorrow morning.

280
00:13:35,030 --> 00:13:36,150
I'm going to Hejin.

281
00:13:36,640 --> 00:13:37,590
I'll need food for the road.

282
00:13:38,790 --> 00:13:40,030
Is it about the Ma Tianjin case?

283
00:13:40,080 --> 00:13:40,880
Yes.

284
00:13:40,910 --> 00:13:42,710
Now Lv Wanchang's son

285
00:13:42,840 --> 00:13:44,080
